srf_paramdesc_views:
{{doc-paramdesc|views}}

The [https://www.semantic-mediawiki.org/wiki/Help:Filtered_format result format "filtered"], part of the Semantic Result Formats extension, displays results in switchable '''views''', e.g. as map, as table, as calendar, etc.

This text is a description of the parameter "views" to the function that generates the "filtered" result format.

Synonyms for '''views''' might be representation, or maybe appearance, aspect, facet
